{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"8892-pel-leng-komsan","title":"ពេលលេងកម្សាន្ត","description":"ហ្គូលូ​ និង ឈូទូ ជាដៃគូ ដែលគួរអោយចង់សើចមួយ។ សូមអាន ពីអាកប្បកិរិយាដ៏ក្រមិុចក្រមើម របស់ មិត្តភក្ដិមួយគូនេះ!","language":"Khmer","langCode":"km","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Khuob  Sopheak"],"illustrators":["Ajit Narayan"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"The Asia Foundation","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/8892-pel-leng-komsan"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/721916/size3/906e74898bf061f7abefb75c6319ad63.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/721916/size6/906e74898bf061f7abefb75c6319ad63.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4632/size6/05d348a35d69e770f33ebc1923eac981.jpg","text":"កូនដំរីតូចមួយឈ្មោះ\nហ្គូលូ។ វាមានរាងមូលដូចស្គរ។ ឯកូនទន្សាយឈ្មោះ ឈូទូ។ វាមានរាងដូចដុំសំឡី។","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4633/size6/3939910b7a0579d539764e852c1da78b.jpg","text":"ពួកគេតែងលេងជាមួយគ្នា។\nថ្ងៃមួយ ហ្គូលូ និយាយថា៖ “តោះថ្ងៃនេះយើងនាំគ្នាលេងល្បែងថ្មី។”","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4634/size6/7cf442bcab4b8b77a04b8952acf05833.jpg","text":"ឈូទូ បង្គាប់ថា៖ “ឯងអង្គុយចុះទៅ។ ខ្ញុំនឹងលោតទៅទំលើខ្នងឯង។”\nហ្គូលូក៏ធ្វើតាម។\nឈូលូលោតយ៉ាងខ្ពស់។","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4635/size6/47c421dba71f4326098256871213ae8d.jpg","text":"ក្ឌុក! វាទំលើខ្នង ហ្គូលូ។\n \nហ្គូលូ សើចរួចនិយាយ៖ “អស្ចារ្យ! ឥឡូវដល់វេនខ្ញុំម្ដង។ ឥឡូវអង្គុយចុះទៅ\nខ្ញុំនឹងលោតទំលើខ្នងរបស់ឯងម្ដង។”","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4636/size6/2a1ed1000db583e991e99cdd5b6d1e08.jpg","text":"“ឯងហ្នឹង!”\n“ត្រូវហើយ គឺខ្ញុំ។”\n“តើឯងគិតធ្វើយ៉ាងម៉េច?” ឈូទូ សួរ។","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4637/size6/58232a7004c248f5ea5ce5d2fdb4ab28.jpg","text":"“ធ្វើបែបនេះ!” ហ្គូលូ ក៏ធ្វើឲ្យមើល។","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4638/size6/4a2f2a72d8ad701133b1e8e23c65674b.jpg","text":"ក្ឌុក...ក្ឌុក...ក្ឌុក\nផ្លែដូងជាច្រើនធ្លាក់ចំក្បាល\nហ្គូលូ។","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4639/size6/0315705cc8174fcbb44d7512317be519.jpg","text":"វាភ័យខ្លាច\nរត់បាតជើងសព្រាត។","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4640/size6/d3c51de81ea2d4bf598492a3441f597b.jpg","text":"ផ្លែដូងតូចមួយធ្លាក់ចំ ឈូទូ។","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/4641/size6/30988ba27514499635a972b370aead1f.jpg","text":"ឈូទូ គិតក្នុងចិត្ត៖\n“គ្រាន់បើបន្តិច។ ដូងធ្លាក់លើប្រសើរជាងដំរីសង្កត់ក្បាល!”","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":10,"words":46}}